644
00:50:28,345 --> 00:50:31,012
Se chegar tarde, ele não te deixa entrar.

645
00:50:31,785 --> 00:50:32,605
Vai logo

646
00:50:34,045 --> 00:50:35,313
Preciso de 5 minutos.

647
00:50:39,095 --> 00:50:39,980
Oi, Khiew.

648
00:50:41,185 --> 00:50:42,251
Eii, Prince.

649
00:50:42,645 --> 00:50:46,645
